The five men were good friends. However, there was one fateful day where one of the men went missing and was never found again...

On a particular Sunday, the men had gathered at the meeting location, which was an old and dilapidated building. They had decided to meet there as no one would overhear what they were talking about since the place was abandoned. They had planned to explore the abandoned hospital opposite the building. After discussing what to do, they set off exactly at midnight.

Upon reaching the hospital, they turned on their torches. It was pitch dark in the hospital. Without the light from their torches, they could easirly end up walking into either the walls or each other. One of the men named Pete shone his torchlight on the wall. On the wall, there were paintings
